{"tid":1333083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB開始意圖幫自己洗白，意味住描起廣告攻勢非常有效","createTime":"2019-07-19T14:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T14:39:05.000Z","uid":22047,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4306edefb7cb6f31ce6af791ee029eb0b2bb33b","tid":1333083,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1332833/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1332833/page/1</a><br />\n講到咁委屈，咪冇撚做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有良心既前線記者得你一間咩，記者永遠都唔夠人架啦，你咪轉去第二間做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n篇文煽情到不得了，又話淚曬新聞部又剩，你估你係十一哥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢篇野有理由懷疑係意圖幫TVB洗白，大家心水清既就知我地既抽起廣告／罷買行動係有成效，並開始對TVB有實質既傷害，所以先出篇咁既野叫我地體諒記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家不能夠心軟，TVB妓者必須繼續狙擊，阻擋拍攝，繼續罷買有落廣告既商品，繼續勸商家抽起廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為TVB同警犬一樣，係過街老鼠，遺臭萬年</span></span>"},{"pid":"057349f22dff54786eed8dce365cbd6abda8be9e","tid":1333083,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:21:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>保障同行手足</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極不建議自行逮捕</span><br />\n但必須當場指出冒警人士<br />\n撲滅罪行 你我有責<br />\n<br />\n【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bb8b0d824699bb807f2b54e2d2b6eed6a7d96552","tid":1333083,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"官媒tvb專心奶共啦。<br />\n<br />\n扮咩野喎"},{"pid":"c23b3396c8aad88ef10bd7089647d3b0ce7cd86f","tid":1333083,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"唔好再比機會返轉頭!!<br />\n今次佢唔收皮就係我地收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e464496ef0a95c08b69b6447332592ffe4700a","tid":1333083,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"想洗白收皮啦！！"},{"pid":"c4ee8238ac3114531f3b5845530a4a1ee70b9de0","tid":1333083,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"ec2daa364151f3aa4ce43cf338926bd08cbed233","tid":1333083,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收皮啦TVB</span></span>"}]}